  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/bb7d91d6e58eb918cef9c30aeaf42e8c.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=278 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Big tribe. Big danger! Monster run. Monsters kills tribe. Player defend. Player kill monsters. Player kill monsters well, get lots of food for defenders. Strong tribe. Player kill monsters bad, monsters kills tribe. Dead tribe, bad player!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/2aafd31a71a96ee9b5b3a4feaf6225c0.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/2aafd31a71a96ee9b5b3a4feaf6225c0.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/2aafd31a71a96ee9b5b3a4feaf6225c0.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player block road, monster stop. Stopped monster, defenders hit easy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/134546b0ffe7a1e896f7bf89eb76fab4.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/134546b0ffe7a1e896f7bf89eb76fab4.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/134546b0ffe7a1e896f7bf89eb76fab4.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defend here. There. Everywhere...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/9797160fbbc17ae7641eaf0dfabc4b04.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=104 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/9797160fbbc17ae7641eaf0dfabc4b04.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/9797160fbbc17ae7641eaf0dfabc4b04.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player use powers. Powers help defenders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/df8e686e924acef6c4cf0ddfd38a075a.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/df8e686e924acef6c4cf0ddfd38a075a.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/df8e686e924acef6c4cf0ddfd38a075a.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If player good, player listen true stories about tribe. No stories for bad player.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/4dbca3131db1eea6bb5ec9adbdf508ca.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/4dbca3131db1eea6bb5ec9adbdf508ca.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/4dbca3131db1eea6bb5ec9adbdf508ca.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There over 100 different kinds? Must strengthen defense!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/e4beb1ce19b79872c3726c592bbaa71a.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=378 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Big Boss. Big Fight. Need many brave man. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/0c3f99b6f1d9e8645478a09025746dee.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/0c3f99b6f1d9e8645478a09025746dee.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/0c3f99b6f1d9e8645478a09025746dee.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many world with many bosses. Each dangerous. Each want eat tribe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/676be0185f8976aa02a2d8e00f464167.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/676be0185f8976aa02a2d8e00f464167.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/676be0185f8976aa02a2d8e00f464167.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defenders. 24 kinds. Different. Think long to choose.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/a622dca18ca8ea51f760c22cb9158f13.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemy sneaky. Enemy use trick. Hard for defender to protect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/e601cabc6aa602e12ccfb0c2eca19d45.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/e601cabc6aa602e12ccfb0c2eca19d45.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/e601cabc6aa602e12ccfb0c2eca19d45.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Must win in different places. Must adapt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/3f0ac4350cab49b15f7551deba9073d8.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/3f0ac4350cab49b15f7551deba9073d8.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/3f0ac4350cab49b15f7551deba9073d8.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good sounds and music in each world. Must enjoy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/a5f32206764b9a558a22d42c4ed55d27.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/a5f32206764b9a558a22d42c4ed55d27.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/a5f32206764b9a558a22d42c4ed55d27.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player smart. Player teach tribe over 100 skills. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/9679488c70ed8b197caa1f101952bb78.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/9679488c70ed8b197caa1f101952bb78.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/9679488c70ed8b197caa1f101952bb78.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player crafty. Player improve defenders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/6ad2e508b05a91ec1d353093c91aa85d.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/6ad2e508b05a91ec1d353093c91aa85d.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/6ad2e508b05a91ec1d353093c91aa85d.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete condition. Earn point. Difficult. Spend point. Gain abilities. Tribe become stronger. Player become proud.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/70962a0f57c2abc383bb2b7fb636b306.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/70962a0f57c2abc383bb2b7fb636b306.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/70962a0f57c2abc383bb2b7fb636b306.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blood. Suffering. Madness! Player be part of this!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/8966f03f8462fd1a68a6f3ea02ad72b3.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/8966f03f8462fd1a68a6f3ea02ad72b3.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/8966f03f8462fd1a68a6f3ea02ad72b3.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player must see all cartoons. Great sense. Big fun!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/bb7d91d6e58eb918cef9c30aeaf42e8c.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=278 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Big tribe. Big danger! Monster run. Monsters kills tribe. Player defend. Player kill monsters. Player kill monsters well, get lots of food for defenders. Strong tribe. Player kill monsters bad, monsters kills tribe. Dead tribe, bad player!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/2aafd31a71a96ee9b5b3a4feaf6225c0.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/2aafd31a71a96ee9b5b3a4feaf6225c0.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/2aafd31a71a96ee9b5b3a4feaf6225c0.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player block road, monster stop. Stopped monster, defenders hit easy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/134546b0ffe7a1e896f7bf89eb76fab4.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/134546b0ffe7a1e896f7bf89eb76fab4.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/134546b0ffe7a1e896f7bf89eb76fab4.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defend here. There. Everywhere...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/9797160fbbc17ae7641eaf0dfabc4b04.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=104 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/9797160fbbc17ae7641eaf0dfabc4b04.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/9797160fbbc17ae7641eaf0dfabc4b04.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player use powers. Powers help defenders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/df8e686e924acef6c4cf0ddfd38a075a.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/df8e686e924acef6c4cf0ddfd38a075a.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/df8e686e924acef6c4cf0ddfd38a075a.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If player good, player listen true stories about tribe. No stories for bad player.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/4dbca3131db1eea6bb5ec9adbdf508ca.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/4dbca3131db1eea6bb5ec9adbdf508ca.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/4dbca3131db1eea6bb5ec9adbdf508ca.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There over 100 different kinds? Must strengthen defense!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/e4beb1ce19b79872c3726c592bbaa71a.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=378 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Big Boss. Big Fight. Need many brave man. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/0c3f99b6f1d9e8645478a09025746dee.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/0c3f99b6f1d9e8645478a09025746dee.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/0c3f99b6f1d9e8645478a09025746dee.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many world with many bosses. Each dangerous. Each want eat tribe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/676be0185f8976aa02a2d8e00f464167.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/676be0185f8976aa02a2d8e00f464167.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/676be0185f8976aa02a2d8e00f464167.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defenders. 24 kinds. Different. Think long to choose.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/a622dca18ca8ea51f760c22cb9158f13.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemy sneaky. Enemy use trick. Hard for defender to protect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/e601cabc6aa602e12ccfb0c2eca19d45.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/e601cabc6aa602e12ccfb0c2eca19d45.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/e601cabc6aa602e12ccfb0c2eca19d45.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Must win in different places. Must adapt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/3f0ac4350cab49b15f7551deba9073d8.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/3f0ac4350cab49b15f7551deba9073d8.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/3f0ac4350cab49b15f7551deba9073d8.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good sounds and music in each world. Must enjoy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/a5f32206764b9a558a22d42c4ed55d27.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/a5f32206764b9a558a22d42c4ed55d27.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/a5f32206764b9a558a22d42c4ed55d27.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player smart. Player teach tribe over 100 skills. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/9679488c70ed8b197caa1f101952bb78.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/9679488c70ed8b197caa1f101952bb78.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/9679488c70ed8b197caa1f101952bb78.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player crafty. Player improve defenders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/6ad2e508b05a91ec1d353093c91aa85d.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/6ad2e508b05a91ec1d353093c91aa85d.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/6ad2e508b05a91ec1d353093c91aa85d.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete condition. Earn point. Difficult. Spend point. Gain abilities. Tribe become stronger. Player become proud.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/70962a0f57c2abc383bb2b7fb636b306.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/70962a0f57c2abc383bb2b7fb636b306.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/70962a0f57c2abc383bb2b7fb636b306.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blood. Suffering. Madness! Player be part of this!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/8966f03f8462fd1a68a6f3ea02ad72b3.poster.avif?t=1765827764\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/8966f03f8462fd1a68a6f3ea02ad72b3.webm?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/603320/extras/8966f03f8462fd1a68a6f3ea02ad72b3.mp4?t=1765827764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player must see all cartoons. Great sense. Big fun!</p>",
